Summary: This section lists the properties available for configuring scene import settings in ResourceImporterScene.

Properties:
*   _subresources (Dictionary): Default: ``{}``
*   animation/fps (float): Default: ``30``
*   animation/import (bool): Default: ``true``
*   animation/import_rest_as_RESET (bool): Default: ``false``
*   animation/remove_immutable_tracks (bool): Default: ``true``
*   animation/trimming (bool): Default: ``false``
*   import_script/path (String): Default: ``""``
*   materials/extract (int): Default: ``0``
*   materials/extract_format (int): Default: ``0``
*   materials/extract_path (String): Default: ``""``
*   meshes/create_shadow_meshes (bool): Default: ``true``
*   meshes/ensure_tangents (bool): Default: ``true``
*   meshes/force_disable_compression (bool): Default: ``false``
*   meshes/generate_lods (bool): Default: ``true``
*   meshes/light_baking (int): Default: ``1``
*   meshes/lightmap_texel_size (float): Default: ``0.2``
*   nodes/apply_root_scale (bool): Default: ``true``
*   nodes/import_as_skeleton_bones (bool): Default: ``false``
*   nodes/root_name (String): Default: ``""``
*   nodes/root_scale (float): Default: ``1.0``
*   nodes/root_script (Script): Default: ``null``
*   nodes/root_type (String): Default: ``""``
*   nodes/use_name_suffixes (bool): Default: ``true``
*   nodes/use_node_type_suffixes (bool): Default: ``true``
*   skins/use_named_skins (bool): Default: ``true``
